aux yeux de tous is a 2012 french thriller film written by audrey diwan and arnaud duprey and directed by cédric jimenez and duprey .   the films stars olivier barthelemy , mélanie doutey and francis renaud .   the films follow a young anonymous hacker who discovers lost security camera footage of a recent terrorist attack at gare d'austerlitz in paris .   he decides to after the culprit and discovers an unexpected plot .